title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 r. 202.70.21 - Courtesy Copies
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 r. 202.70.21 - Courtesy Copies

State Regulations

Courtesy copies should not be submitted
unless requested or as herein provided. However, courtesy copies of all motion
papers and proposed orders shall be submitted in cases in the court's Filing by

Electronic Means System. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22
r. 202.70.21. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
